# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT ignored — it is committed for
